@ Osean:

The International Coalition of Aces, also known as TICA, is a secret organization composed of aces from across the planet, the most known examples are Mobius 1, Cipher, Pixy, PJ, Gryphus 1, Warwolf 1, and countless aces, TICA was formed after the Lighthouse War as a form of keeping peace via going in sabotage missions to undermine, eliminate, and cover-up any possible threat to peace, the leader of this organization is none other than Mobius One, the ace of the Continental War, he is well-known across the IUN for his efforts in the two Free Erusea uprisings, the organization does not operate on a ranking system despite Mobius One leading the Organization.

So I learned about this, and while ignoring the pretty long sentence (I'm guilty of it too, so I'm not saying this negatively, hehe), the fact that there's an organisation of ace pilots helping defend the planet. Taking inspiration from Ace Combat, and with your own flavor, it's kinda like Overwatch or Rainbow Six as well, heh. The world could always use more covert heroes.
